==English==

===Alternative spellings===
*[[whigger]]

===Etymology===
{{wikipedia}}
[[Portmanteau]] of ''[[white]]'' and ''[[nigger]]'' or ''[[wannabe]]'' and ''nigger.''

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{informal}} {{derogatory}} A [[white]] person (typically [[young]] and [[male]]) who dresses, speaks, or otherwise behaves in a manner that is stereotypically associated with certain aspects of African-American, Caribbean or hip-hop culture.